ZH: 我买了个新的兜儿来装我的东西。
EN: I bought a new bag to carry my stuff in.

ZH: 他每天都背着一个很大的兜儿。
EN: He carries a big bag on his back every day.

ZH: 这个兜儿很结实，可以装很多东西。
EN: This bag is very sturdy and can hold a lot of things.

ZH: 她把钥匙放在了兜儿里。
EN: She put the keys in the bag.

ZH: 孩子们很开心地拿着兜儿四处跑。
EN: The children happily ran around with their bags.

ZH: 我的兜儿里装着我的手机和钱包。
EN: My bag contains my phone and wallet.

